{"tid":1312401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"謀殺生命，是我們的職責","createTime":"2019-07-13T13:36:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T14:05:33.000Z","uid":195,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"404439abd7a17289127babe78b995b0b5095801d","tid":1312401,"uid":195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:36:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ScCGmUX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FScCGmUX.png&h=e2e1eef6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【謀殺生命】<br />\n<br />\n在今晚 (2019-07-13) 約八時半，一名約十六歲男子因被警察追打，幾乎墮橋。警方接報後，迅速趕到現場，並將有關男子即場拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n謀殺生命，是你們的職責？<br />\n<br />\nAt about 2030 hours on 2019-07-13, a sixteen-year-old teenager was chased and beaten by police. The boy nearly fell off the bridge.  As such, Police made expeditious arrival to scene upon report and arrested the boy decisively.<br />\n<br />\nIs your duty to kill life?<br />\n<br />\n#HKPpolicing"},{"pid":"eb40ec0a4d9ac7fd2216a0493cd11010dd23915e","tid":1312401,"uid":195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:42:02.000Z","msg":"聽日沙田見！"},{"pid":"c02d7d3da21661a3243004639a71e4f9b3641bf2","tid":1312401,"uid":195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:42:38.000Z","msg":"Fuck the popo"},{"pid":"15171e530f2a0ea5ca642bc515422f9cd03333a7","tid":1312401,"uid":11804,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:43:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"393d46d2e8b324ab193c273b807fd05cd3235a81","tid":1312401,"uid":195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"15171e530f2a0ea5ca642bc515422f9cd03333a7","tid":1312401,"uid":11804,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:43:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T13:44:15.000Z","msg":"無黑警今日會好和平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beeaf18c561503ff5f73d157f7ed2d4246d7e8ba","tid":1312401,"uid":11804,"like":0,"disl